name: Fancy File Renamer
tagline: A fancy little tool for renaming a bunch of files at once
body:
### Welcome to Fancy File Renamer
Ever needed to rename a lot of files all at once? This program can do the work for you. It allows you to replace, enumerate, insert text to a bunch of files. Before starting to rename you can preview your changes. You can even sort the files before renaming.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
